Quote:Yeah, I have no idea what I'm going to do for food during that.Fruit. Bring any two of an apple, orange, or pear and you've got something that will hold you over until you leave the venue and can get something relatively light and filling. Cut em or peel em in the hotel room and put them in some zip loc baggies (almonds are also good) and throw them in your rucksack.I find it impossible to believe that someone at such a large convention wouldn't sell some fresh fruit, too, if they prohibit you bringing any food items in.
